STATE of North Carolina.
v.
Tracy Lamont CLARK. No. 13P11-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Aug. 20, 2015. Teresa M. Postell, Assistant Attorney General, for State of N.C. Tracy Lamont Clark, for Clark, Tracy Lamont. Philip E. Berger, Jr., District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 20th of May 2015 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Rockingham County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 20th of August 2015."
